DataList.LocalizeEN: Don't worry if you're breathing.

DataList.LocalizeEN: I got some delicious food.

DataList.LocalizeEN: Everyone, let's make it time to eat

DataList.LocalizeEN: Even though you can't eat it.

DataList.LocalizeEN: It's not your turn.

DataList.LocalizeEN: Will I be able to make more delicious rice with this?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 先生と一緒に過ごす時間はお料理をしてる時と同じくらい楽しいです。

DataList.LocalizeJP: 最高の香辛料は優しく愛。
DataList.LocalizeEN: The best spice is kindness and love.

DataList.LocalizeEN: I'm worried about what kind of ingredients I should put in order to express this happiness with taste.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 先生と一緒に食べるお料理ならどのようなお料理でも美味しいです
DataList.LocalizeEN: Any kind of food is delicious as long as you eat it with your teacher.
